{"type":"card","data":{"approach":"Note that the feasible function checks whether the element is greater than or equal to the target. But the question asks for the index of the first element exactly equal to the target. Our template updates ans = mid whenever arr[mid] >= target. Therefore, we have to make a small modification to the template and move ans = mid to only when arr[mid] == target and not arr[mid] >= target.","difficulty":6.7299999999999995,"due":1784527332027,"elapsed_days":0,"historyLog":[1783009646633,1783009646633,1783576932027],"id":"1783009646633","lapses":0,"lastRating":4,"reps":2,"scheduled_days":11,"spaceComplexity":"","stability":5.8,"state":2,"tags":["Binary Search"],"textRead":"","timeComplexity":"","u":30}}
